2):[5] Cerner Multum, Inc. "UK Summary of Product Characteristics." O 0[6] Cerner Multum, Inc. "Australian Product Information." O 0[7] "Product Information. Ritalin LA (methylphenidate)." Quality Care Products/Lake Erie Medical  (2013):[8] "Product Information. Azstarys (dexmethylphenidate-serdexmethylphenidate)." Corium, Inc.  (2021):', 1767369485);
